#1 Problem:
  Player randomly teleports into random positions when moving up and down with the platform.
  This happened due to me using 2 ways of making the player move with the platform. One was keeping the player with the platform sprite. 

  "if abs(player_values["x"] - plat_values["x"]) < 5: 
        player_values["y"] = plat_values["y"] - 8"

  and manually updating the players vertical height 

  "if player_on_plat_x and player_on_plat_y and plat_moving_down:
    if ycoordPlayer > 0:
        ycoordPlayer -= 1
        player_values["y"] = playery[ycoordPlayer]"  <----- This line


Solution:
  I only make the keeping the player on the platform logic move the sprite and only use the manual updating of the players vertical height to keep track of which platform level the player is currently on. 



  
